{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_22","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed and escalated for `io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5`.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-1410-library-new-request-io.smallrye-jandex-3.0.5-8067b7a4\n\nThe most likely failing stage was test generation / native-test verification, followed by an environment-sensitive `generateMetadata` retry. Evidence:\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T04-22-18-263613Z.log` shows `:nativeTest` failing in `StrongInternPoolTest.serializesPoolWithEntries()` with `java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: org.jboss.jandex.StrongInternPool`.\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T04-33-35-540924Z.log` shows the next retry failing in `IndexerTest.indexClassReadsLoadedClassResource()` with `java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: stream cannot be null`.\n- Later reruns passed, and `stats/io.smallrye/jandex/3.0.5/stats.json` reports dynamic-access coverage at 5/5 (100.00%).\n- The remaining escalation appears to come from `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/metadata-fix/codex.log`, where nested `generateMetadata` fails with `Could not find agent library native-image-agent ... libnative-image-agent.so`.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/metadata-fix/codex.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T04-22-18-263613Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T04-33-35-540924Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-05T04-49-06-265357Z.log`\n- `stats/io.smallrye/jandex/3.0.5/stats.json`\n- `stats/io.smallrye/jandex/3.0.5/execution-metrics.json`\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch diff and confirm it stays scoped to `metadata/io.smallrye/jandex/3.0.5` and `tests/src/io.smallrye/jandex/3.0.5`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5` and `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=io.smallrye:jandex:3.0.5 --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar` with nested Gradle forced onto the same GraalVM so `native-image-agent` is available.\n3. If those reruns stay green, promote the preserved metadata/test changes; otherwise fix the remaining environment/test-generation issue before opening a PR."}}
